      <p outputclass="ps_para_number" id="UUID-799d96c5-afd4-f8e0-6b3e-b8f5fd164736_aag-afi11.12" class="- topic/p ">
         <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">11.12</b> The fair
                    value, intrinsic value, and time value of the put option are as follows:</p>
      <table outputclass="ruled" id="UUID-799d96c5-afd4-f8e0-6b3e-b8f5fd164736_aag-afi11_table3" class="- topic/table ">
         <tgroup cols="4" class="- topic/tgroup ">
            <colspec colname="c1" align="left" class="- topic/colspec "/>
            <colspec colname="c2" align="right" class="- topic/colspec "/>
            <colspec colname="c3" align="right" class="- topic/colspec "/>
            <colspec colname="c4" align="right" class="- topic/colspec "/>
            <thead class="- topic/thead ">
               <row class="- topic/row ">
                  <entry class="- topic/entry "/>
                  <entry align="center" valign="bottom" class="- topic/entry ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">
                        <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">(A)</i>
                        <ph class="- topic/ph ">
                           <fn callout="3" id="UUID-799d96c5-afd4-f8e0-6b3e-b8f5fd164736-aag-afi11-fn3" class="- topic/fn ">
                              <p class="- topic/p ">The fair value may be based on observable prices,
                                            recent transactions, third-party pricing services,
                                            broker or dealer quotes, or models prepared by
                                            management or management’s specialists. See additional
                                            guidance on techniques that management may use to value
                                            financial instruments in <xref format="dita" class="- topic/xref " href="../../../../aag-afi/aag-afi1/aag-afi1_valuation_of_financial_instruments/aag-afi1_effects_of_inactive_markets/aag-afi1_effects_of_inactive_markets.dita#UUID-6fb2258c-c136-40b1-b87c-df36644428fb_UUID-58c3eab9-3ea9-b89c-2826-bfa56db7e9d6/UUID-6fb2258c-c136-40b1-b87c-df36644428fb_aag-afi1.33">paragraphs 1.33–.55</xref> of this guide.</p>
                           </fn>
                           <xref type="fn" class="- topic/xref " href="aag-afi11_description_of_the_transaction.dita#UUID-799d96c5-afd4-f8e0-6b3e-b8f5fd164736_UUID-6cc0ec83-f22c-b0be-1910-5ada68d03f21/UUID-799d96c5-afd4-f8e0-6b3e-b8f5fd164736-aag-afi11-fn3"/>
                        </ph>
                     </p>
                     <p class="- topic/p ">
                        <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">Fair Value</i>
                     </p>
                  </entry>
                  <entry align="center" valign="bottom" class="- topic/entry ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">
                        <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">(B)</i>
                        <ph class="- topic/ph ">
                           <fn callout="4" id="UUID-799d96c5-afd4-f8e0-6b3e-b8f5fd164736-aag-afi11-fn4" class="- topic/fn ">
                              <p class="- topic/p ">Intrinsic value is computed based on the changes in
                                            spot rates as compared with the strike rate.</p>
                           </fn>
                           <xref type="fn" class="- topic/xref " href="aag-afi11_description_of_the_transaction.dita#UUID-799d96c5-afd4-f8e0-6b3e-b8f5fd164736_UUID-6cc0ec83-f22c-b0be-1910-5ada68d03f21/UUID-799d96c5-afd4-f8e0-6b3e-b8f5fd164736-aag-afi11-fn4"/>
                        </ph>
                     </p>
