                  </entry>
                  <entry align="right" valign="bottom" class="- topic/entry ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">238,095 <ph class="- topic/ph ">
                           <fn callout="5" id="UUID-799d96c5-afd4-f8e0-6b3e-b8f5fd164736-aag-afi11-fn5" class="- topic/fn ">
                              <p class="- topic/p ">Foreign currency [FC] 10,000,000 ÷ 2.00 = $5,000,000)
                                            less (FC 10,000,000 ÷ 2.10 = $4,761,905) =
                                            $238,095.</p>
                           </fn>
                           <xref type="fn" class="- topic/xref " href="aag-afi11_description_of_the_transaction.dita#UUID-799d96c5-afd4-f8e0-6b3e-b8f5fd164736_UUID-6cc0ec83-f22c-b0be-1910-5ada68d03f21/UUID-799d96c5-afd4-f8e0-6b3e-b8f5fd164736-aag-afi11-fn5"/>
                        </ph>
                     </p>
                  </entry>
                  <entry align="right" valign="bottom" class="- topic/entry ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">10,000</p>
                  </entry>
               </row>
               <row class="- topic/row ">
                  <entry align="left" valign="bottom" class="- topic/entry ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">March 31, 20X2</p>
                  </entry>
                  <entry align="right" valign="bottom" class="- topic/entry ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">652,174</p>
                  </entry>
                  <entry align="right" valign="bottom" class="- topic/entry ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">652,174 <ph class="- topic/ph ">
                           <fn callout="6" id="UUID-799d96c5-afd4-f8e0-6b3e-b8f5fd164736-aag-afi11-fn6" class="- topic/fn ">
                              <p class="- topic/p ">(FC 10,000,000 ÷ 2.00 = $5,000,000) less (FC
                                            10,000,000 ÷ 2.30 = $4,347,826) = $652,174. The increase
                                            in intrinsic value is $414,079 ($652,174 less
                                            $238,095).</p>
                           </fn>
